Hi, kindly ensure the below points before accessing UPI:
1. UPI/BHIM will only function on the Bank Registered Mobile no.
2. The Registered Mobile number has to be in SIM 1 in case of a Dual sim phone.
3. Registered mobile no. should have sufficient balance for SMS to go.
4. Ensure that registered mobile no. is the default sim for sending SMS.
5. HDFC Bank Mobilebanking App is updated in PlayStore / App store. Also, as per UPI guidelines, to ensure higher security, the UPI registration has to be completed by User in 30 seconds, beyond that the registration process will drop and the user has to re-initiate the registration. -Team MobileBanking
